1
00:00:50,383 --> 00:00:51,885
I'll ask, you answer.

2
00:00:52,519 --> 00:00:54,020
If you hesitate for even a second,

3
00:00:54,421 --> 00:00:55,421
or if you lie,

4
00:00:56,556 --> 00:00:57,796
then you can show yourself out.

5
00:01:03,696 --> 00:01:05,865
Did you get into this industry for me?

6
00:01:06,399 --> 00:01:07,399
Yeah.

7
00:01:09,636 --> 00:01:10,804
Then why didn't you admit it?

8
00:01:11,805 --> 00:01:12,806
There was no point.

9
00:01:14,641 --> 00:01:15,641
Fine.

10
00:01:17,477 --> 00:01:19,279
Let's go back to the start.

11
00:01:21,047 --> 00:01:22,382
Why did you ghost me?

12
00:01:31,591 --> 00:01:32,591
Are you gonna talk?

13
00:01:33,526 --> 00:01:35,027
Three... two...

14
00:01:35,028 --> 00:01:36,388
I didn't want to ruin your future.

15
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:38,231
Ruin my future? My ass.

16
00:01:39,065 --> 00:01:40,732
I hadn't even debuted yet.

17
00:01:40,733 --> 00:01:42,202
What, are you psychic?

18
00:01:43,336 --> 00:01:45,038
If I hadn't locked my phone,

19
00:01:45,872 --> 00:01:47,207
what were you planning to do?

20
00:01:49,142 --> 00:01:50,809
I'd just make an excuse and act busy.

21
00:01:50,810 --> 00:01:52,212
We'd never met in person anyway.

22
00:01:53,279 --> 00:01:55,159
Well, you're the one who
wouldn't send a photo.

23
00:01:55,348 --> 00:01:56,615
When you were in that accident

24
00:01:56,616 --> 00:01:57,716
and I wanted to visit you,

25
00:01:57,717 --> 00:01:58,877
you turned me down then, too.

26
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:01,086
Because I didn't want to just be friends.

27
00:02:01,087 --> 00:02:02,967
I was afraid I wouldn't
be able to help myself.

28
00:02:03,957 --> 00:02:05,692
I was afraid of being a stain on your life.

29
00:02:07,227 --> 00:02:08,587
Whether you're a "stain" or not...

30
00:02:09,262 --> 00:02:10,996
is for me to decide.

31
00:02:10,997 --> 00:02:12,632
You're too loyal for your own good.

32
00:02:12,866 --> 00:02:14,032
I didn't want people

33
00:02:14,033 --> 00:02:15,673
to look at you differently because of me.

34
00:02:15,768 --> 00:02:17,503
I didn't want you to
give up on your dreams,

35
00:02:17,504 --> 00:02:19,464
and I didn't want to be
the one holding you back.

36
00:02:23,610 --> 00:02:24,377
Everything you just said,

37
00:02:24,378 --> 00:02:25,879
all those worries,

38
00:02:26,613 --> 00:02:28,147
assume that I actually like you.

39
00:02:29,182 --> 00:02:31,017
Aren't you getting ahead of yourself?

40
00:02:32,752 --> 00:02:34,420
You never even confessed to me.

41
00:02:35,555 --> 00:02:36,995
How could you possibly hold me back?

42
00:02:42,095 --> 00:02:43,563
You're the heir to Baili.

43
00:02:44,063 --> 00:02:45,797
I was just a student on financial aid.

44
00:02:45,798 --> 00:02:47,333
The gap between us was already huge.

45
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:49,234
Then you said you were going into showbiz,

46
00:02:49,235 --> 00:02:50,436
and I really started to panic.

47
00:02:50,937 --> 00:02:52,472
So I got into this business

48
00:02:53,273 --> 00:02:54,541
just to be closer to you.

49
00:02:55,742 --> 00:02:57,243
But the more fans you got,

50
00:02:58,144 --> 00:02:59,479
the more I lost my nerve.

51
00:02:59,812 --> 00:03:00,812
So...

52
00:03:01,781 --> 00:03:03,616
you used this short film as a chance

53
00:03:04,183 --> 00:03:05,351
to give yourself a keepsake?

54
00:03:07,053 --> 00:03:08,053
You went through all that trouble

55
00:03:08,054 --> 00:03:08,821
just to drag me into

56
00:03:08,822 --> 00:03:10,490
the story of A-You and Youzhi.

57
00:03:10,890 --> 00:03:11,890
Yeah.

58
00:03:13,259 --> 00:03:14,259
That way, I could...

59
00:03:16,095 --> 00:03:17,775
I could at least pretend we had something.

60
00:03:25,004 --> 00:03:26,673
And that's enough for you?

61
00:03:31,044 --> 00:03:32,044
Why are you trying so hard

62
00:03:32,045 --> 00:03:33,580
to be some tragic hero?

63
00:03:36,149 --> 00:03:38,051
No wonder your A-You chose to leave.
